==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: holier-than-thou
<hw>holier-than-thou</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>being excessively or
hypocritically pious while condemning others as being less virtuous than
oneself.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> pietistic, pietistical, pharisaic, pharisaical,
sanctimonious, self-righteous.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Holily</ent>⟦br⟧
